{"tid":2431907,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"確診翁或播毒美心MX等至少2藍店 嘉里控股秘書染疫食simplylife 帶病吃米芝蓮一星","createTime":"2021-03-04T03:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T08:09:31.000Z","uid":239336,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"823ce298c58b2b624f84aaf962c8d88743abf21c","tid":2431907,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心披露，周三（3日）新增的其中2宗源頭不明確診，傳染期（發病前2日起計）行蹤頗多。其中住柴灣的69歲退休男，除傳染期去過美心MX和麗香園冰室2間藍店，由發病當日至3日後，更去過4間餐廳。至於住康城的53歲嘉里控股女秘書，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">除傳染期去過藍店美心旗下的simplylife，又帶病前往曾奪米芝蓮一星的南海一號，發病後8日仍到鰂魚涌嘉里中心上班。嘉里控股所有同事都要強制檢測。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n防護中心和醫管局多次提醒市民，武漢肺炎除有不少播毒的隱形患者，亦不乏病徵輕微的帶毒者，呼籲市民即使只有極輕微病徵，都應盡早求醫和檢測，以及盡量留家，避免外出和聚會。此外，以往有不少患者經醫生診斷後，被要求交樣本樽或前往採樣，但未待檢測結果就頻密外出，結果增加確診前的接觸史，容易傳染他人。防護中心亦屢次呼籲市民，即使等候檢測結果，仍應避免外出，盡量留家。<br />\n<br />\n第11044號個案<br />\n●69歲退休男子，住柴灣興華（二）邨裕興樓。<br />\n<br />\n●他2月27日發病，頭痛。<br />\n<br />\n●<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">他傳染期去過柴灣和筲箕灣多家餐廳；25日去新翠商場藍店美心MX，26日去興華商場藍店麗香園冰室、永利中心群記爽腩店，27日發病當日去興華商場民華餐廳，28日仍去H21商場明星金閣，3月1日去大家樂旗下一粥麵的新翠商場分店，3月2日去工廠街德福樓地下和興華商場大快活。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第11047號個案<br />\n●53歲嘉里控股女秘書，在鰂魚涌嘉里中心32樓上班，住將軍澳日出康城緻藍天翠堤。<br />\n<br />\n●她2月22日發病，咳嗽和喉嚨痛，至3月1日樣本檢測結果呈陽性，但2日才最後上班。<br />\n<br />\n●<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">她傳染期去過去過多家餐廳和商廈；20日去美心旗下藍店simplylife BAKERY CAF&Eacute;的九龍灣德福廣場1期分店、大家樂旗下oliver&rsquo;s SUPER SANDWICHES的德福廣場2期分店，22日發病當日去中環萬邦行，26日仍去將軍澳PopCorn Greyhound Caf&eacute;，27日去曾奪米芝蓮一星的尖沙嘴iSQUARE南海一號、灣仔凱聯紅花會，28日去將軍澳TKO Gateway。</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2F24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE%2F&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX4MLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=8632f142\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2F24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE%2F&h=c6d52f7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/24SJCFTR6ZA5PHNTLWDPPEOBNE/</a>"},{"pid":"2282ca741e408999e0aad39c4585fcc5d75824d0","tid":2431907,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:24:54.000Z","msg":"D廢老廢中特別鍾意要人陪葬，真攬炒"},{"pid":"12208cf0d18246c0720f9a696a6a0fa676aa6912","tid":2431907,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e5c9132274d1eaef59feeb52c0c6b7f3ab7de5","tid":2431907,"uid":13308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:34:06.000Z","msg":"抵撚死呀仆街藍屍"},{"pid":"6d1925fa77d14d5aa59bf967e6bb9c2c4ea9d6e3","tid":2431907,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f443d7aa0025eb91e6c3916821f85df6ff7733b5","tid":2431907,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:35:29.000Z","msg":"藍屍藍店中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b13eed2900310a9fac12dc6c9695e8f99bc8a3","tid":2431907,"uid":390224,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"1個53碎，1個69碎，唔怪得放棄年青人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ace902439f14f8bf75